      "text": "He was a big, big [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] He was really to be like a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] to be a rabbi, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] and I was living near by him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
