    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were all the-- well, there was a-- a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] You see-- but they are taking water here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
