      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said I see you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say to him, I will ask [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Oh, then you must have known [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Gohara. ?] The name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Gohara. ?] I would, but why are you asking, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I say, this [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Gohara ?] is my mother's uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh, sure, nobody ever said we are the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, are you mother, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Lerner ?] was it your mother's from [INAUDIBLE] Yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then I tell you, he say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SOB] He gives unto me dreidel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He maybe somebody in the Jewish people who are alive-- give this away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, now, there's no better man than you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You say it's your mother's uncle.",
